answer:
A complete series of the HPV9 vaccine is recommended to ensure protection against the five additional HPV types in the vaccine. If you received the HPV vaccine for free as part of B.C.'s publicly-funded program, you would need to purchase the additional doses. We recommend that you discuss this further with your immunizing health care provider. 
Immunization Nurse
